headline: These e-commerce companies are gaining back 'tremendous' share
summary: While Adobe Analytics expects consumers to spend a record $14.2 billion on Cyber Monday purchases, Shopify (SHOP) experienced an outage that disrupted online shopping and caused login issues for merchants around the world. Wedbush managing director of equity research Scott Devitt discusses the performance of e-commerce platforms and websites as the holiday shopping season kicks off. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
